Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:19.88,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}若能变得更强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.57,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}眼前的这个天空
